By adding the Bot to your server or interacting with it, you agree to comply with and be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, you must stop using the Bot and remove it from your server.

2. Eligibility and Compliance
To use the Bot, you must comply with Discord’s Terms of Service and Community Guidelines. You can review Discord’s Terms of Service at:
https://discord.com/terms

and Discord’s Community Guidelines at:
https://discord.com/guidelines

If you are prohibited from using Discord, you are not permitted to use the Bot.

3. Acceptable Use
You agree not to use the Bot in any way that violates Discord’s policies or applicable law. This includes, but is not limited to:

. Using the Bot for harassment, hate speech, discrimination, or abusive content

