. We reserve the right to restrict or terminate your access if these rules are broken.

4. Service Availability
The Bot is provided “as is” and “as available.” We make no guarantees that the Bot will be available at all times or that it will operate without errors. The Bot may be updated, changed, or discontinued at any time without notice.

5. Data Collection and Use
The Bot may temporarily process and store limited information such as:

