Server IDs

Message content used for specific commands (if applicable)

Command usage statistics

This data is only used to operate the Bot’s features and is not sold or shared with third parties. No personal information is permanently stored unless explicitly stated. For more details, refer to the Privacy Policy.

6. Privacy
We value your privacy. Any data collected by the Bot is used solely to provide its intended functionality. Sensitive information will never be disclosed, shared, or used for purposes unrelated to the Bot.

