You understand and agree that we are not liable for any damages, disputes, or losses that may occur from using the Bot. This includes, but is not limited to, server disruption, loss of data, or conflicts between users. By using the Bot, you agree to hold the developer(s) harmless against any claims or damages.

8. Termination of Access
We reserve the right to deny access to the Bot, remove the Bot from servers, or blacklist users or servers at our discretion. This may occur without prior warning and may be due to violations of these Terms, abuse, or other misuse of the Bot.

9. Changes to Terms
